data.description: SELLER MOTIVATED!!! SELLER LOWERED 5k !!!THIS Two Possible Three BEDROOM, TWO and HALF BATH with bonus room TOWNHOME HAS ITS' OWN PRIVATE ELEVATOR! The first level has tons of closet storage, covered lanai, outdoor fenced patio . This is one of the Largest units in the community! Cement Block Construction! DOUBLE MASTER SUITES ! FOR BUYERS PURCHASING THIS HOME,OUR NEIGHBORHOOD HOUSING PROGRAM OFFERS THE ABILITY TO PURCHASE A HOME WITH LOWER DOWN PAYMENT AND NO PMI. Taking the elevator to the second level you are greeted with your kitchen. KITCHEN IS OPEN TO THE DINING AREA & FAMILY ROOM, THAT HAS A BALCONY. KITCHEN FEATURES 42" MAPLE ESPRESSO CABINETS WITH 2" CROWN MOULDING, STAINLESS APPLIANCES & GRANITE COUNTERTOPS WITH AN UNDERMOUNT STAINLESS SINK. COMPETING THE second LEVEL IS A DEN (could be a third bedroom) WITH A WALK-IN CLOSET & A POWDER ROOM. BEDROOMS ARE ON THE Third LEVEL. MASTER BEDROOM HAS A WALK-IN CLOSET & MASTER BATH WITH UPGRADED WALL TILE, GRANITE COUNTERTOP & DOUBLE SINKS. BEDROOM TWO HAS AN EN SUITE BATH WITH TUB AND WALK IN CLOSET. THIS COMMUNITY HAS ACCESS TO A PRIVATE BEACH . There are 2 Pools with the first pool having a cabana and bathrooms, One pool also boasts a Gym . Gated entry to the neighborhood for privacy. LOW HOA fees for the community! Fees cover: Cable TV, Common Area Taxes, Community Pool, Escrow Reserves Fund, Internet, Maintenance Exterior, Maintenance Grounds, Maintenance Repairs, Pest Control, Pool Maintenance, Private Road, Recreational Facilities, Trash This home has CLOSET STORAGE SPACE!Assumable FHA mortgage of $173,000. 5.5% fixed for 30 years Penny Mac is the lender. $183,000 down needed. currently PIMI payment $1565
